 style=\"color: red;\">用最少資源做到最大效益<br />\n港鐵快跑運動<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">急停制/路軌/車長室/火警鐘撳手</span>等等<br />\n分3/4 team人可癱瘓一個上午</span><br />\n港鐵車長/站長可<span style=\"color: red;\">按章工作</span><br />\n幫幫忙盡量拖延時間<br />\n香港人需要你</span></span>"},{"pid":"8ee47a1a97095c9a8a81691c39725ef92ad39012","tid":1405190,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd0294812a9591ab9e2366e30ad9f5a36a9e7173","tid":1405190,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:00:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推推推 推上去</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zMjXBH7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzMjXBH7.png&h=9acfb023&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf139253cfee9d6c33ff250bc9ac642de6e9c2ec","tid":1405190,"uid":167592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:26:34.000Z","msg":"推"}]}